  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether immunoadsorption of LPS, Il-6 and C5a
      reduces systemic hyperinflammation, improves immune function and improves organ function in
      patients with severe sepsis and septic shock
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
